# Release (1.3.0) Summary
The following changes are contributed by @rirurin :)

- Added an option to skip the intro movie when switching to Epsidoe Aigis
- Fixed an issue where the opening movie plays when switching from Ep Aigis to base game regardless of the option set
- Added an option to enable fast navigation. This lets you start making inputs immediately, similar to how Metaphor's title screen works.

